section.section:
"Small community college" means:
Allegany College of Maryland;
Garrett College;
Hagerstown Community College;
Carroll Community College;
Cecil Community College;
Chesapeake College; or
Wor-Wic Community College.

Subject to subsection (d) of this section, the total State share for each board shall be the sum of:
The fixed costs component;
The marginal costs component;
The size factor component; and
A hold harmless component.

Subject to paragraph (4) of this subsection, the unrestricted grants shall be distributed as follows:
$500,000 to Allegany College of Maryland;
$500,000 to Garrett College;
$500,000 to Hagerstown Community College;
$250,000 to Carroll Community College;
$250,000 to Cecil Community College;
$250,000 to Chesapeake College; and
$250,000 to Wor-Wic Community College.
